#: ../../talk/call_recording.rst:2
msgid "Call recording"
msgstr "Taifeadadh glaonna"

#: ../../talk/call_recording.rst:4
msgid "The recording feature lets you:"
msgstr "Ligeann an ghné taifeadta duit:"

#: ../../talk/call_recording.rst:6
msgid "Start and stop recordings during a call."
msgstr "Tosaigh agus stop taifeadtaí le linn glao."

#: ../../talk/call_recording.rst:7
msgid ""
"Record the video and audio stream of the speaker, as well as screen share."
msgstr ""
"Taifead sruth físe agus fuaime an chainteora, chomh maith le comhroinnt "
"scáileáin."

#: ../../talk/call_recording.rst:8
msgid ""
"Access, share and download recorded files for future reference or "
"distribution."
msgstr ""
"Rochtain a fháil ar chomhaid taifeadta, iad a roinnt agus a íoslódáil le "
"haghaidh tagartha nó dáilte sa todhchaí."

#: ../../talk/call_recording.rst:10
msgid ""
"Enabling this feature requires the recording server to be set up by the "
"system administration."
msgstr ""
"Chun an ghné seo a chumasú, ní mór don riarachán córais an freastalaí "
"taifeadta a shocrú."

#: ../../talk/call_recording.rst:13
msgid "Manage a recording"
msgstr "Bainistigh taifeadadh"

#: ../../talk/call_recording.rst:15
msgid ""
"The moderator of the conversation can start a recording together with a call"
" start or anytime during a call:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir le modhnóir an chomhrá taifeadadh a thosú in éineacht le tús glao "
"nó am ar bith le linn glao:"

#: ../../talk/call_recording.rst:17
msgid ""
"**Before the call**: tick the checkbox \"Start recording immediately with "
"the call\" in \"Media settings\", then click on \"Start call\"."
msgstr ""
"**Roimh an nglao**: cuir tic sa bhosca seiceála \"Tosaigh ag taifeadadh "
"láithreach leis an nglao\" i \"Socruithe meán\", ansin cliceáil ar \"Tosaigh"
" glao\"."

#: ../../talk/call_recording.rst:18
msgid ""
"**During the call**: click on the top-bar menu, then click \"Start "
"recording\"."
msgstr ""
"**Le linn an ghlao**: cliceáil ar an roghchlár sa bharra uachtarach, ansin "
"cliceáil \"Tosaigh ag taifeadadh\"."

#: ../../talk/call_recording.rst:28
msgid ""
"The recording will start shortly, and you will see a red indicator next to "
"the call time. You can stop the recording at any time while the call is "
"still ongoing by clicking on that indicator and selecting \"Stop "
"recording\", or by using the same action in the top-bar menu. If you do not "
"manually stop the recording, it will end automatically when the call ends."
msgstr ""
"Tosóidh an taifeadadh go luath, agus feicfidh tú táscaire dearg in aice le "
"ham an ghlao. Is féidir leat an taifeadadh a stopadh am ar bith agus an glao"
" fós ar siúl trí chliceáil ar an táscaire sin agus \"Stop an taifeadadh\" a "
"roghnú, nó tríd an ngníomh céanna a úsáid sa roghchlár barr an bharra. Mura "
"stopann tú an taifeadadh de láimh, críochnóidh sé go huathoibríoch nuair a "
"chríochnaíonn an glao."

#: ../../talk/call_recording.rst:33
msgid ""
"After stopping a recording, the server will take some time to prepare and "
"save the recorded file. The moderator, who started the recording, receives a"
" notification when the file is uploaded. From there, it can be shared in the"
" chat."
msgstr ""
"Tar éis stop a chur le taifeadadh, tógfaidh sé tamall ar an bhfreastalaí an "
"comhad taifeadta a ullmhú agus a shábháil. Gheobhaidh an modhnóir, a "
"thosaigh an taifeadadh, fógra nuair a uaslódálfar an comhad. As sin, is "
"féidir é a roinnt sa chomhrá."

#: ../../talk/call_recording.rst:44
msgid "Recording consent"
msgstr "Toiliú taifeadta"

#: ../../talk/call_recording.rst:46
msgid ""
"For compliance with privacy regulations, it is possible to ask participants "
"for consent to be recorded before joining the call. Administrators can "
"configure this feature in several ways:"
msgstr ""
"Chun cloí le rialacháin phríobháideachais, is féidir toiliú a iarraidh ar "
"rannpháirtithe le go dtaifeadfaí iad sula nglacfaidh siad páirt sa ghlao. Is"
" féidir le riarthóirí an ghné seo a chumrú ar roinnt bealaí:"

#: ../../talk/call_recording.rst:48
msgid "Disable consent completely."
msgstr "Díchumasaigh toiliú go hiomlán."

#: ../../talk/call_recording.rst:49
msgid ""
"Enable mandatory consent system-wide, requiring consent for all "
"conversations."
msgstr ""
"Cumasaigh toiliú éigeantach ar fud an chórais, agus éilítear toiliú do gach "
"comhrá."

#: ../../talk/call_recording.rst:50
msgid ""
"Allow moderators to configure this option on a conversation level. In such "
"cases, moderators can access the conversation settings to configure this "
"option accordingly:"
msgstr ""
"Lig do mhodhnóirí an rogha seo a chumrú ar leibhéal comhrá. I gcásanna den "
"sórt sin, is féidir le modhnóirí rochtain a fháil ar shocruithe an chomhrá "
"chun an rogha seo a chumrú dá réir:"

#: ../../talk/call_recording.rst:57
msgid ""
"If recording consent is enabled, every participant, including moderators, "
"will see a highlighted section in the \"Media settings\" before joining a "
"call. This section informs participants that the call may be recorded. To "
"give explicit consent for recording, participants must check the box. If "
"they do not give consent, they will not be allowed to join the call."
msgstr ""
"Má tá toiliú taifeadta cumasaithe, feicfidh gach rannpháirtí, lena "
"n-áirítear modhnóirí, cuid aibhsithe sna \"Socruithe Meán\" sula nglacfaidh "
"siad páirt i nglao. Cuireann an chuid seo rannpháirtithe ar an eolas go "
"bhféadfaí an glao a thaifeadadh. Chun toiliú sainráite a thabhairt le "
"haghaidh taifeadta, ní mór do rannpháirtithe an bosca a sheiceáil. Mura "
"dtugann siad toiliú, ní cheadófar dóibh páirt a ghlacadh sa ghlao."
